                <div class="blog-text-column">
                    <span class="blog-date">September 28, 2025</span>
                    <h3 class="blog-title">Zina & Zain</h3>
                    <p class="blog-excerpt">
                        From floating shikaras on Dal Lake to traditional Kashmiri rituals under chinar trees, Zina and Zain's wedding was a dream to witness and document. We focused on capturing the soft morning mist, the rich embroidery of their traditional garbs, and the quiet intimacy of their vows...
                    </p>
                    <a href="#" class="blog-read-more">Read Story</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Post 3: Image Left, Content Right -->
            <div class="blog-post-row fade-in-section">
                <div class="blog-img-column img-zoom-wrapper" style="box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);">
