                </div>
                <div class="blog-text-column">
                    <span class="blog-date">July 05, 2025</span>
                    <h3 class="blog-title">Alya & Yahia</h3>
                    <p class="blog-excerpt">
                        A breathtaking desert dune sunset ceremony in Dubai, followed by an intimate candle-lit dinner under the stars. The vast expanse of the red sands and the shifting wind created a stunning backdrop for their vows, allowing us to experiment with shadow and dramatic silhouettes...
                    </p>
                    <a href="#" class="blog-read-more">Read Story</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Post 5: Image Left, Content Right -->
            <div class="blog-post-row fade-in-section">
                <div class="blog-img-column img-zoom-wrapper" style="box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);">
